snippet.title: Freedom9
snippet.description:
Brand © Freedom9

Dear Friends, My name is Viktor Angelovski and welcome to my channel.

I created this channel in 2011 Into Deep house, Rnb, Jazz and chill remixes that I love and since than, my music has reached all regions in Balkan and also worlwide. Supporting and promoting magnificent producers and labels releases.
Enjoy the Beats of the Music from Amazing artists.

I would never be where I am today without all of your support. Thank you so much to anyone for spending your precious time and listening to my work and subscribing to my channel, I am forever grateful, Viktor Angelovski.

if you want to join the community, just tap the subscribe button! 
Also please, make yourself at home. Freedom9 music is just getting started.

#Freedom9 #Deephouse #Rnb #Jazz


All business enquiries and contact email below:
viktorpe4urka@gmail.com
